        <li>Exercise</li>
      </ul>
    </slide>
    <slide id="what-is-api-design-review">
      <title>What is API Design : Review</title>
      <ul>
        <li>Defines your API</li>
        <li>Gives meaning/purpose to your work</li>
        <li>Acts as a guide while building</li>
        <li>Provides a reference for users</li>
      </ul>
    </slide>
    <slide id="api-story-review">
      <title>API Story : Review</title>
      <ul>
        <li>Structured MD</li>
        <li>Purpose, Properties, Resources, Actions, Rules</li>
        <li>Design guidance, shared understanding</li>
      </ul>
    </slide>
