				<ul>
					<li>MCP seems to be the new <q>standard protocol</q> for LLM consumers</li>
					<li>Many mapping tools to generate MCP from OpenAPI descriptions</li>
					<li>Complex APIs will overload the MCP host's context</li>
					<li>Larger API landscapes will overload the MCP host's context</li>
				</ul>
